00:00:25.620 --> 00:00:32.782
The title of my talk is How to Sell with Noble
Purpose, and so I'm gonna give you the big

00:00:32.782 --> 00:00:35.610
idea at the very front end.

00:00:35.610 --> 00:00:41.399
And the idea is this: the salespeople who
sell with a sense of higher purpose, that

00:00:41.399 --> 00:00:46.780
is the salespeople who are what I call the
true believers, who believe not only in their

00:00:46.780 --> 00:00:51.370
products but who also believe in the impact
that they have on their customers, that they

00:00:51.370 --> 00:00:57.339
make a difference in the lives of their customers,
those salespeople outperform the salespeople

00:00:57.339 --> 00:01:01.760
who are just focused on their quotas or the
money.

00:01:01.760 --> 00:01:07.630
And these words selling and noble, a lot of
people don't think that they go together,

00:01:07.630 --> 00:01:14.040
in fact, a lot of people think that sales
is anything but noble and when you call someone

00:01:14.040 --> 00:01:17.730
"salesy" it's not really a compliment [chuckles]
in most cases.

00:01:17.730 --> 00:01:22.030
But I'm here to tell you that they're wrong,
because when they talk about sales from that

00:01:22.030 --> 00:01:26.990
perspective they're really just talking about
the number side, the quota side, the spreadsheet

00:01:26.990 --> 00:01:27.990
side.

00:01:27.990 --> 00:01:31.460
And so what I'm wanna talk to you about is
the whole other side of sales.

00:01:31.460 --> 00:01:34.160
And so I wanna share with you the research
I've done and the results of the research

00:01:34.160 --> 00:01:39.820
I've done for the last 10 years that prove
beyond a shadow of a doubt that when you have

00:01:39.820 --> 00:01:44.950
a larger purpose, when you're part of something
that's bigger than you are, when you know

00:01:44.950 --> 00:01:53.030
that what you're doing makes a difference,
you're more effective, you're more assertive,

00:01:53.030 --> 00:01:55.640
you're most successful, and you're also happier.

00:01:55.640 --> 00:01:56.640
[pause]

00:01:56.640 --> 00:02:02.490
And nowhere is this more important than in
sales, because the reality of sales is you

00:02:02.490 --> 00:02:08.330
may have a target, a quota, whatever language
you use, that connects with your head.

00:02:08.330 --> 00:02:14.650
But when you have a sense of a higher purpose
it connects with your heart which is where

00:02:14.650 --> 00:02:16.450
your passion lies.

00:02:16.450 --> 00:02:21.330
So I'm gonna make you three promises for today,
I hear a motorcycle revving up [bad audio]

