number one I'm gonna show you how you can

00:02:27.280 --> 00:02:33.790
bring a sense of purpose and passion to your
job, how you can fall in love with your job;

00:02:33.790 --> 00:02:37.700
number two I'm gonna show you how you can
bring that sense of purpose to your customers,

00:02:37.700 --> 00:02:43.230
to get your customers more engaged; and number
three how you can bring it to the other areas

00:02:43.230 --> 00:02:45.520
of your life and the people that you care
about.

