So I sold advertising and then I was the sales
manager for the college newspaper.

00:06:13.250 --> 00:06:17.800
And when I was 20 years old I was the sales
manager and our college newspaper sold a million

00:06:17.800 --> 00:06:20.120
dollars worth of advertising in one year.

00:06:20.120 --> 00:06:23.550
Now I know that's nothing compared to what
you all sell, but for a college newspaper

00:06:23.550 --> 00:06:27.580
that is a lot of money [chuckles] that is
like an unheard of amount of money.

00:06:27.580 --> 00:06:29.710
So clearly I was on fire for sales.

00:06:29.710 --> 00:06:34.410
So after college I went to work for Proctor
&amp; Gamble, I was a salesperson there, won some

00:06:34.410 --> 00:06:38.020
