00:10:10.630 --> 00:10:16.230
So again what was that thing, what was that
thing that made them different?

00:10:16.230 --> 00:10:17.230
So then –

00:10:17.230 --> 00:10:18.550
[sound of papers being shuffled]

00:10:18.550 --> 00:10:21.480
another typical way, call frequency and call
