[pause]

00:11:06.769 --> 00:11:12.529
They always make a lot of calls and they're
significant calls, they're of a length enough

00:11:12.529 --> 00:11:14.300
to get some depth with the customer.

00:11:14.300 --> 00:11:18.800
So we looked at that and of course those were
the people who had really great sales calls,

00:11:18.800 --> 00:11:25.510
but again there were a couple people in there
