they just felt different, there was that thing,

00:11:35.190 --> 00:11:36.330
that thing again.

00:11:36.330 --> 00:11:37.610
What was that thing?

00:11:37.610 --> 00:11:42.660
So we were getting close to the end of the
project and I was with this one sales rep

00:11:42.660 --> 00:11:45.030
