community activist, and she talked about how

00:23:27.720 --> 00:23:30.109
she'd made a difference in the community.

00:23:30.109 --> 00:23:34.840
I and her other children spoke about how she'd
made a difference to us.

00:23:34.840 --> 00:23:40.489
And I just remember sitting there thinking,
"This is what everybody wants; everybody wants

00:23:40.489 --> 00:23:45.679
to know that their life really matters."

00:23:45.679 --> 00:23:49.149
And perhaps you've had this similar experience
at a funeral where you're sitting there thinking,

00:23:49.149 --> 00:23:54.940
