heard this."

00:24:04.450 --> 00:24:08.639
I don't know if you've ever had that experience
at a funeral where you're just amazed when

00:24:08.639 --> 00:24:11.309
you add up the sum of a person's life.

00:24:11.309 --> 00:24:15.909
Wow, they had a really big impact.

00:24:15.909 --> 00:24:21.049
And so that moment was when I realized that
