so that really led me on a search for meaning

00:24:30.509 --> 00:24:35.799
and purpose and to find ways to infuse that
into everything I did.

00:24:35.799 --> 00:24:42.419
And it's a shame when we miss it, when we
miss what a big impact we have.

00:24:42.419 --> 00:24:45.440
I said I'm sitting there thinking, "Gosh I
wonder if my mother even knew this," and in

00:24:45.440 --> 00:24:46.610
all likelihood she didn't.

00:24:46.610 --> 00:24:48.360
The reality was she probably didn't.

00:24:48.360 --> 00:24:53.599
'Cause what happens is we get so busy with
our day to day lives and we do this and we

00:24:53.599 --> 00:24:56.200
