actually having on all the people around us.

00:25:02.359 --> 00:25:06.229
And we fail to appreciate what a difference
we actually do make.

00:25:06.229 --> 00:25:10.919
And this is real shame, it's a shame for two
really important reasons: it's a shame because

00:25:10.919 --> 00:25:17.490
we don't get to experience the joy of knowing
how much we matter and so we miss it; and

00:25:17.490 --> 00:25:24.200
it's also a shame because when we don't realize
the impact that we have on other people we're

00:25:24.200 --> 00:25:28.509
not as intentional in the way that we interact
