00:58:58.740 --> 00:58:59.970
It works; there's nothing wrong with that.

00:58:59.970 --> 00:59:02.650
What I wanna give you is a different mental
model.

00:59:02.650 --> 00:59:06.520
And you all have the book in front of you
so if you think salesperson/customer, different

00:59:06.520 --> 00:59:10.690
mental model is what we call the Triangle
of Truth and it's thinking about your sales

00:59:10.690 --> 00:59:13.999
calls in a very different way.

00:59:13.999 --> 00:59:18.140
Your sales calls are no longer I'm trying
to get the customer over to my agenda, you're

00:59:18.140 --> 00:59:24.079
sales calls are in service of your NSP, your
noble sales purpose.

00:59:24.079 --> 00:59:29.780
So if I'm showing up to help my customers
be more successful or if I'm showing up to

00:59:29.780 --> 00:59:36.390
help customers find my customers then everything
single thing I do on that sales call is in

00:59:36.390 --> 00:59:38.970
service of that.

00:59:38.970 --> 00:59:40.840
Why is this so important?

00:59:40.840 --> 00:59:45.320
This is important because one of the things
that salespeople struggle with is being able

00:59:45.320 --> 00:59:51.950
to master the, I wanna help the client and
I need to close this deal; that quagmire right

00:59:51.950 --> 00:59:52.950
there.

00:59:52.950 --> 00:59:56.789
What this does it is says you can do both
because the most successful salespeople, in

00:59:56.789 --> 01:00:01.380
the studies I did with salespeople, the most
successful people have a both/and mentality.

