&gt;&gt;Lisa Earle McLeod: Right.

01:05:30.473 --> 01:05:31.473
How are we gonna do this?

01:05:31.473 --> 01:05:33.720
And typical, I mean I've been a sales manager,
typical conversation, "When are we gonna close

01:05:33.720 --> 01:05:34.720
