01:06:38.430 --> 01:06:40.989
Because it matters, now it matters.

01:06:40.989 --> 01:06:42.640
I can't wait for their lives to be different.

01:06:42.640 --> 01:06:44.910
I wanna have this impact on them.

01:06:44.910 --> 01:06:46.210
It matters.

01:06:46.210 --> 01:06:49.070
And if you can't paint a positive picture
of how their lives will be different you are

01:06:49.070 --> 01:06:52.170
probably not going to close it anyway.

01:06:52.170 --> 01:06:54.849
[chuckles] So that one question.

01:06:54.849 --> 01:06:57.019
Can you hear the difference in what that does?

01:06:57.019 --> 01:07:00.259
Remember, what do you do when you described
