01:07:00.259 --> 01:07:02.080
It was about why you did it.

01:07:02.080 --> 01:07:08.470
This is about the why and that transforms
that sales manager conversation.

01:07:08.470 --> 01:07:11.640
[pause]

01:07:11.640 --> 01:07:17.420
This is the reality: quotas, targets, numbers,
they connect with your head.

01:07:17.420 --> 01:07:22.400
When you have a sense of purpose it connects
with your heart.

01:07:22.400 --> 01:07:28.820
And top performing salespeople have both;
they're very clear on the numbers, but they're

01:07:28.820 --> 01:07:34.319
also very clear on how they make a difference
to their customers and that's what they keep

01:07:34.319 --> 01:07:36.380
at the front and center.

01:07:36.380 --> 01:07:39.559
And so that leads me to the third thing that
I told 'ya I was gonna talk to you about which

01:07:39.559 --> 01:07:44.769
is how you pull this sense of purpose to the
front and center of all your relationships,

01:07:44.769 --> 01:07:47.450
not just with your customers.

01:07:47.450 --> 01:07:53.789
'Cause see here's a little secret: when you
know that you're interactions with other people

01:07:53.789 --> 01:07:59.309
make a difference, when you know that your
life matters, that you make a difference,

01:07:59.309 --> 01:08:07.109
you show up for it in a much bigger way; you
show up in a bigger way.

01:08:07.109 --> 01:08:11.710
You show up as your best version of yourself.

01:08:11.710 --> 01:08:16.740
Because having a sense of purpose in your
life is actually how you start to fall in

01:08:16.740 --> 01:08:21.730
love with your own life 'cause that's when
you know it matters.

01:08:21.730 --> 01:08:22.730
[pause]

01:08:22.730 --> 01:08:26.839
So your work matters, your company matters,
your life matters, you matter.

01:08:26.839 --> 01:08:35.389
And one of the biggest mistakes that we make
is we undervalue our lives and the impact

01:08:35.389 --> 01:08:40.900
that we have on other people; it's a huge
mistake 'cause when you bring a sense of purpose

01:08:40.900 --> 01:08:46.630
and you know that you make a difference everything
changes, everything changes.

01:08:46.630 --> 01:08:52.450
And so I want you to keep that in your mind:
that your job matters, your company matters,

01:08:52.450 --> 01:08:59.699
your life matters, and you matter, everything
that you do matters, it matters a lot.

